cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper deals with detecting image repurposing, which involves analyzing the metadata associated with images. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimodal learning (cs.MM). The paper also involves knowledge base integration (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) to extract related information. Additionally, the paper deals with detecting nefarious activity (cs.CR) on social media platforms.
